    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cuckoo’s Clock is a difficult puzzle platformer all about controlling the speed of the level around you. Slow down gears to make it through tight gaps or speed up treadmills to fling you across the stage!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316180/extras/ec69301c2dbfa72458e687789ce6e9c1.avif?t=1733850336\" width=612 height=306 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A series of 12 stages, or “hours” to complete. Each with a hard to collect feather for those skilled enough to obtain it!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A good ending obtained by collecting all 12 feathers!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >30+ unlockable skins for you to customize Cuckoo with!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A variety of speedrun challenges to overcome, requiring a mastery of both the speed up and slow down mechanics!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Several unique contraptions and obstacles working in tandem with each other!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >And more...</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316180/extras/74fceef8e2174e0109ccaa01a3948b25.avif?t=1733850336\" width=612 height=304 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Threats loom in every corner of the clock! Can you make it out and escape to safety?</p>",
